# Apertium Ido-Esperanto Translation Pair

This package provides translation capabilities between Ido and Esperanto using the Apertium machine translation platform.

## Features

- Bidirectional translation between Ido and Esperanto
- Proper number handling in translation pipeline
- Basic morphological analysis and generation
- Bilingual dictionary with core vocabulary

## Installation

```bash
./configure --prefix=/usr/local
make
sudo make install
```

## Usage

After installation, you can use:

```bash
echo "En oktobro 1782 Durrani mortis pro naturala kauzi." | apertium ido-epo
echo "En oktobro 1782 Durrani mortis pro naturaj kaÅ­zoj." | apertium epo-ido
```

## Requirements

- Apertium >= 3.4.0
- lttoolbox >= 3.3.2
- apertium-ido (monolingual Ido package)
- apertium-epo (monolingual Esperanto package)

